        "8460f45c-7563-483f-badf-2257b330af1c": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "headline": "BASIC INFO",
            "content": "<p>Need something? We got you. For questions about orders, products, ingredients, training, pricing or anything else, our team is here for you with answers.<\/p><p>Our Customer Service team is available Monday-Friday 9am–5:30pm ET.<\/p><p>You can use online Chat, complete an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.animalpak.com\/contact\">online form here<\/a>, call us at 800-872-0101 or email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@animalpak.com\">info@animalpak.com<\/a>.<\/p><p>For any questions regarding training, diet, and supplementation email us at <a href=\"mailto:trainer@animalpak.com\">trainer@animalpak.com<\/a>.<\/p><p>Emails and chats sent during non-business hours will be read on the next business day and responded to in order of receipt. Your patience is appreciated.<\/p><p><strong>Mailing Address<\/strong><\/p><p>Customer Service Department<br\/>3 Terminal Road<br\/>New Brunswick, NJ 08901<\/p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "a23bfc99-5afa-4056-be2d-82ab54ccc3d7": {
          "type": "content",
